By Olaitan Ganiu  Known for showing off her hips, Nollywood actress Biodun Okeowo who goes by the moniker Omobutty has, again, posted another eye-popping picture on Instagram. In the image, the sexy actress was seen wearing a jump suit as she shows her backside. “Never hate people who are jealous of you, but respect their jealousy because they’re the ones who think you’re better than them,” she captioned the picture.  “One with God is a majority.” Biodun who hit the limelight when she acted a movie titled ‘Tolai Osinrin’, once revealed she married as a virgin. She had two children for her ex-husband before they separated.